-- Patent Wars Hit Social Media as Yahoo Sues Facebook
-- B y
-- 2012-03-13T13:32:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-13/patent-wars-hit-social-media-as-yahoo-sues-facebook.html
Bloomberg's Cris Valerio reports 
that Facebook Inc. was accused in a lawsuit by Yahoo! Inc. of 
infringing patents covering functions critical to websites, 
including  Internet advertising , information sharing and 
privacy. She speaks on Bloomberg Television's "In The Loop." 
(Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 01:52
 